title: George H.W. Bush tosses 1st pitch at Game 3 of ALDS
text:
> Texas George H.W. Bush tosses 1st pitch at Game 3 of ALDS Former President George H.W. Bush throws out the ceremonial first pitch to Houston Astros' Jed Lowrie before Game 3 of baseball's American League Division Series against the Kansas City Royals Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015, in Houston. (AP Photo/David J. Phillip) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
